Now the Trump White House is targeting the Statue of Liberty.
The most reliable sign of regime change is when it starts fighting the statues.
Americans understand this as well as anyone else, and that's why the theatrical demolition of the statue of Saddam Hussein in Firdous Square in Baghdad in 2003 was done.
Steven Miller, one of the key ideologues in the Trump administration, no doubt knew what he was doing when he brandished a symbolic ax over the Statue of Liberty during a fierce debate with CNN reporter Jim Acosta over the president's proposals to drastically reduce legal immigration.
